Cell["\<\
We have rules for the derivatives of the normal spinor. Here \[CapitalOmega]4 \
is the symmetric trace-free part of the second fundamental form, and \
\[CapitalOmega]0 the trace. AccNn is the acceleration. We have assumed that \
the normal is hypersurface orthogonal.\[LineSeparator](Expressions for the \
definitions should be added to the package.)\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9586995144768906`*^9, 3.9586996331225243`*^9}, {
  3.958699727545145*^9, 3.958699748654972*^9}, {3.9586998286927357`*^9, 
